Description: Vehicle Modbus monitor daemon and client
 oati-ts-monitor polls Modbus TCP controllers, optional GNSS/Wi‑Fi enrichment,
 an HTTP dashboard, JSONL logging, and a local IPC socket for CLI/TUI clients.
